==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
#(''US'') {{slang}} A soft, warm, and typically [[fuzzy]] blanket or [[garment]] that is used simply for its comfortable characteristics.
#(''US'') {{slang}} A [[cuddly]], soft, and [[fuzzy]] stuffed toy, usually in the form of some [[adorable]] animal.

